  <brief_title>A Pharmacokinetic And Safety Study Of Voriconazole In Healthy Male And Female Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Intravenous (6/4 Mg/Kg Q12h) To Oral Switch (200 Mg Q12h), Multiple Dose Study To Evaluate The Pharmacokinetics, Safety And Tolerability Of Voriconazole In Healthy Male And Female Adults</official_title>
  <sponsors>
